⚡Shortly

A modern frontend-only URL shortener web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

Shortly allows users to instantly convert long URLs into short links and generate QR codes for easy sharing, all directly in the browser without requiring any backend server.

---

🚀 Features

* 🔗 Instant URL shortening using the TinyURL API
* 📋 One-click copy to clipboard
* 📱 Automatic QR code generation for shortened links
* 💾 Option to download QR codes
* ⚡ Fast and lightweight performance
* 🎨 Clean and modern user interface
* 📱 Fully responsive design for mobile and desktop

---

🛠 Tech Stack

* HTML5
* CSS3
* Vanilla JavaScript
* TinyURL API
* QR Server API
* Font Awesome Icons

---

📦 Project Structure

Shortly/
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── app.js
└── README.md


---

⚙️ How It Works

1. The user enters a long URL into the input field.
2. The application sends the URL to the TinyURL API.
3. TinyURL returns a shortened version of the link.
4. The shortened link is displayed on the screen.
5. A QR code is generated automatically for quick sharing.
6. Users can copy the link, open it, or download the QR code.

---

🌐 Running the Project

To run the project locally:

1. Download or clone the repository.
2. Open the file: index.html

The application will run directly in your browser.

You can also deploy it using GitHub Pages.

